{
  "stem": "5758.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know whether the Germans entered there, had a camp, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I couldn't find anything, none whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Said, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He took me to the station again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I took the train to Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must tell you something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, for instance, if I think about it, it said how stupid one can be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm in the unoccupied zone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I go into the lion's den.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was, as a young fellow, without fear whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was completely-- I was naive and young and without fear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wanted a cello.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, when I was in-- picking up the-- the-- the-- the-- the train, you know, to go to Paris, and then on the train I said to me, you're going to Paris and change the train to go to Limoges.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I must be-- you must be mad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, you have never seen Paris-- the Eiffel Tower, Arc de Triomphe, the Champs-Elysees, Place Pigalle, the night life of Paris.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You must go and see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How can I as a-- how could I have done this, you know, without any fear whatsoever, without even thinking about it?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's so stupid now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nowadays, when I-- how stupid can a young person be?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I must say, I was very young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is actually how I arrived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
